This paper deals with interference in mobile wireless networks, which is a topic related to networked systems (cs.SY) and mobile ad hoc networks (cs.MA). The paper also discusses the impact of blockage on interference, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and wireless networking (cs.NI). Finally, the paper uses simulations to analyze the results, which is a topic related to multimedia (cs.MM). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.NI, followed by cs.IT, cs.MA, cs.SY, and cs.MM.
